OL,4,Cmistreated by owner
OL,6,FA man has been banned from keeping
OL,7,Fanimals for 10 years after eight dogs
OL,8,Fwere found in inhumane conditions with
OL,9,Fcuts and scars to their faces.
OL,11,FReece Robertson pleaded guilty to four
OL,12,Foffences under the Animal Welfare Act
OL,13,F2006.
OL,15,FHe given the ban, along with a 12
OL,16,Fmonth community order, requiring him
OL,17,Fto complete 200 hours of unpaid work.
OL,18,FHe was also ordered to pay costs of
OL,19,F#500.
