OL,6,FThe court was told RSPCA officers and
OL,7,Fpolice found eight dogs at Robertson's
OL,8,Fhome in Millom, Cumbria and at a
OL,9,Fnearby allotment, several of the dogs
OL,10,Fwere suffering from untreated wounds.
OL,12,FRSPCA Chief Inspector Ian Muttit said
OL,13,Fthree adult dogs and a puppy were kept
OL,14,Fin very poor conditions in kennels
OL,15,Flocated in Robertson's back garden.
OL,17,FThe dogs included a bull lurcher
OL,18,Fcalled Barn, a female bull lurcher
OL,19,Fcalled Bella, Patterdale terrier
OL,20,Fcalled Punch and a lurcher puppy.
