OL,4,Cmistreated by owner
OL,6,FChief Inspector Muttit said: "Each
OL,7,Fkennel was small and the run areas had
OL,8,Flarge amounts of faeces built up
OL,9,Finside, while the sleeping areas for
OL,10,Feach were extremely basic and looked
OL,11,Finadequate in terms of shelter or
OL,12,Fbedding."
OL,14,FRSPCA officers found five more dogs in
OL,15,Ffive separate kennels, including a
OL,16,Ffemale lurcher who had lost part of
OL,17,Fher nose and had scars across her
OL,18,Fface. Also suffering with facial cuts
OL,19,Fand scars were a Patterdale terrier, a
OL,20,Ffemale lurcher and two male lurchers.
