OL,6,FRobertson indicated he had not
OL,7,Fattended the allotment for two to
OL,8,Fthree days and no arrangements were
OL,9,Fmade for anyone to attend to the dogs.
OL,10,FAll eight dogs were seized and taken
OL,11,Fto the care of the RSPCA.
OL,13,FRobertson, of Cook Road in Millom,
OL,14,Fsaid none of the dogs were under a vet.
OL,16,FIn mitigation, the court heard
OL,17,FRobertson had learning difficulties
OL,18,Fand was "regarded as a soft touch for
OL,19,Fanimals in the area".
